/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees, providing a stark contrast to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the road, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. The sky overhead is a blanket of overcast clouds, casting a soft, diffused light over the scene. The predominant colors in the image are shades of green from the trees and gray from the buildings and road, creating a harmonious blend of nature and architecture.
